title: One Bedroom Apartment *Convenience & Value at Garden View*
posting_body: ['One bedroom apartment available!', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'to schedule a personal viewing or stop by Monday-Friday between 9am to 6pm or Saturday- Sunday between 10am to 3pm to view an open model.', 'Our apartments include large patios and balconies.', 'Every unit includes a dishwasher, ceiling fan and air conditioner.', 'Laundry facilities are conveniently located on each floor, no quarters needed!', 'Heat, water, sewer and garbage fees are all included in your monthly rent.', 'Single stall garages are also available!', 'Our residents love our great recreation facilities, including an indoor and outdoor pool, rec room with billiards tables, 2 playgrounds, fitness center and party room.', 'We offer the best value and amenities in New Brighton!', 'Please call or come by for a look at our units.', 'Application fee: $45', "Deposit: one month's rent", 'Pets: Up to 2 cats with additional deposit', 'Directions: I-694 to Silver Lake Road.', 'South on Silver Lake Road to 7th', 'Street NW, turn left.', '7th Street NW 1/2 mile to 8th Street NW, turn left.', 'Property is on the left.', 'Office Location:', '1417 10th St NW', 'New Brighton, MN 55112', 'Please call us at', 'show contact info', 'Keywords: New Brighton, Shoreview, Arden Hills, Roseville, Columbia Heights, Fridley, Mounds view, Minneapolis, Freedom Park, Pike lake, 35W, 694, Lake Jones, Long lake, Round lake, Shoreview, Cedarholm, Blain, Coon Rapids, Brooklyn Parks']
